name: All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Leslie Road, Essendon - Boxes 2022/01/11
description:
All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Leslie Road, Essendon - Boxes - 2022/01/11
The "All the Hidden Quanta - Postcard from ..." series using Processing visual arts language, explores the concept that we are surrounded by the unseen (unacknowledged? unrealised?), constantly in flux world of quanta. This project was processed from real time camera captures during the afternoon of Tuesday January 11, 2022. mp4, 1280x960px, 25fps, 50seconds(please loop), 68.1MB.
